      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and offers a fantastic balance of utility and value! While you\u2019ll find some expected wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid performer that\u2019s perfect for daily commuting or as a dependable second car. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a functional vehicle at a price that makes sense!",
