    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a very reliable choice for a daily driver. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major odors or tears, though you will find some light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. The exterior still shines beautifully, but a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light scuffing on the rear bumper. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
